Review_body:
So basically film has some pros and cons and I will start with pros. Pros of the movie:*It looks visually perfect;
*The actors are persuasive;
*Nice name of the movie;
*The ending which I didn't expect(I believed that the main actor(android dude) is going to be the chosen one but it wasn't :O);Cons of the movie:*Too much attention has been given to insignificant things;
*Didn't like the episode of ballerina which was created by CCCP(film shouldn't promote returning of CCCP);
*I didn't understand why the main leader of androids(a blind guy) is killing other androids if he said that there are not enough of them. It seems illogical;To sum up the film wasn't so bad I would recommend it for everyone because it was interesting despite its cons.
